Name: Name Change, Ellen Sidlar, R.N. Playground, Borough of Queens.
Title: A Local Law in relation to a playground name, Ellen Sidlar, R.N. Playground, Borough of Queens.
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:
Section 1.  The following street name is hereby designated as hereafter indicated.

New Name				Present Name			Limits

Ellen Sidlar, R.N. 	Turtle Playground	an existing playground located 
Playground 								on the triangle formed by the 
south side of the eastbound service road of the Long Island Expressway at 138th Street and 61st Street
      
      
      ï¿½  2.  This local law shall take effect immediately.
